      "order": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "<p>De omzetting van <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi data-mjx-auto-op=\"false\">FeCl</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>2</mn>&#160;</mrow></msub></math>tot <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi data-mjx-auto-op=\"false\">Fe</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>2</mn> </mrow></msub><msub><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi> </mrow><mrow data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><mn>3</mn>&#160;</mrow></msub></math>verloopt volgens reactie 1 .</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>FeCl</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">g</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">g</mi><mo>)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">&#8594;</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>Fe</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mi>HCl</mi><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">g</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mtext>(reactie 1)&#160;</mtext></math></p><p>Reactie 1 verloopt zeer snel onder de omstandigheden in de reactor.</p>"
